Implementation of word2vec [1] and paragraph vectors [2] in C++

Required external libraries
- google log (glog)
- OpenBLAS
- Boost

compiler
- g++11

References

[1] Tomas Mikolov, Ilya Sutskever, Kai Chen, Greg Corrado, and Jeffrey Dean. Distributed Representations of Words and Phrases and their Compositionality. NIPS, 2013.
[2] Quoc V. Le and Tomas Mikolov, Distributed Representations of Sentences and Documents, ICML, 2014.
